3#ifndef __NVKM_ENGINE_H__
4#define __NVKM_ENGINE_H__
5#define nvkm_engine(p) container_of((p), struct nvkm_engine, subdev)
6#include <core/subdev.h>
7struct nvkm_fifo_chan;
8struct nvkm_fb_tile;
9
10struct nvkm_engine {
11 const struct nvkm_engine_func *func;
12 struct nvkm_subdev subdev;
13 spinlock_t lock;
14
15 int usecount;
16};
17
18struct nvkm_engine_func {
19 void *(*dtor)(struct nvkm_engine *);
20 int (*oneinit)(struct nvkm_engine *);
21 int (*init)(struct nvkm_engine *);
22 int (*fini)(struct nvkm_engine *, bool suspend);
23 void (*intr)(struct nvkm_engine *);
24 void (*tile)(struct nvkm_engine *, int region, struct nvkm_fb_tile *);
25
26 struct {
27 int (*sclass)(struct nvkm_oclass *, int index,
28 const struct nvkm_device_oclass **);
29 } base;
30
31 struct {
32 int (*cclass)(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *,
33 const struct nvkm_oclass *,
34 struct nvkm_object **);
35 int (*sclass)(struct nvkm_oclass *, int index);
36 } fifo;
37
38 const struct nvkm_object_func *cclass;
39 struct nvkm_sclass sclass[];
40};
41
42int nvkm_engine_ctor(const struct nvkm_engine_func *, struct nvkm_device *,
43 int index, u32 pmc_enable, bool enable,
44 struct nvkm_engine *);

47 struct nvkm_engine **);

49void nvkm_engine_unref(struct nvkm_engine **);
50void nvkm_engine_tile(struct nvkm_engine *, int region);
51#endif
